name: Ke Badholy
description:
Ke Badholy is a friendly demon that protects you from hatred, uncompassion, and lying too much.

Each guardian demon is created by combining hundreds of unique elements, colors, patterns, and randomly generated designs. The demons do not represent evil, but rather ward off evil like gargoyles on a cathedral.

Collect a demon to protect you against evil and to remind you that you can overcome your personal demons no matter how many or how frightening they might be.
